00:00:00.330 --> 00:00:04.165
Birinchi bo‘lib activity_numbers.xml 
faylini o‘zgartiraman,

00:00:04.165 --> 00:00:06.428
GridView XML elementini saqlash uchun.

00:00:06.428 --> 00:00:10.638
Ya’ni ListView ni GridView ga o‘zgartiraman.

00:00:10.638 --> 00:00:14.922
Hozir men, yangi android numbers column 
nomli atributni qo‘shishim kerak,

00:00:14.922 --> 00:00:18.798
va bu yerda grid nechta ustunga ega 
bo‘lishini aniqlashingiz mumkin,

00:00:18.798 --> 00:00:20.570
masalan, men 2 ni tanlayman.

00:00:22.450 --> 00:00:24.370
E’tibor bering, oldindan ko‘rish panelida,

00:00:24.370 --> 00:00:28.290
Android Studio bu qanday ko‘rinishga 
kelishini ko‘rsatishga harakat qiladi.

00:00:28.290 --> 00:00:31.290
Yana bir bor qaytarib o‘taman,
 bu bizning ilovamizning ma’lumotlarini

00:00:31.290 --> 00:00:34.490
 ko‘rsatmaydi, va biz ishlatayotgan 
 elementlar ro‘yxati ham emas.

00:00:34.490 --> 00:00:37.853
Buning yagona maqsadi, grid da 
ikkita ustun bo‘lishini va qanchalik 

00:00:37.853 --> 00:00:39.488
yaxshi ko‘rinishga ega 
bo‘lishini ko‘rsatish.

00:00:39.488 --> 00:00:43.356
Yaxshi, keling NumbersActivity.java ga
 qaytamiz va

00:00:43.356 --> 00:00:45.338
men hozir bu yerda xato ko‘ryapman.

00:00:45.338 --> 00:00:49.430
Xato xabar unexpected cast 
ListView da borligini aytyapti, 

00:00:49.430 --> 00:00:52.828
chunkitag layout faylida
 GriedView deb nomlangan. 

00:00:52.828 --> 00:00:57.215
Biz, GriedViewga o‘tganimiz uchun,
Layout da view ni topib 

00:00:57.215 --> 00:01:01.348
uni GridView ga otib, o‘zgaruvchida 
GridView turi ostida saqlab qo‘yishimiz kerak. 

00:01:01.348 --> 00:01:02.768
Keling shu o‘zgarishni hozir kiritamiz.

00:01:02.768 --> 00:01:05.001
[AUDIO YO‘Q]

00:01:05.001 --> 00:01:07.638
Yaxshi, endi xatoliklar yo‘q, va butun
 kod va uning faoliyati ham

00:01:07.638 --> 00:01:09.240
 yaxshi ko‘rinyapti.

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:11.452
Va biz array list ni 
odatdagidek yaratishimiz mumkin va

00:01:11.452 --> 00:01:14.750
ArrayAdapter ni so‘zlar ro‘yxatidan 
yaratishimiz ham mumkin.

00:01:14.750 --> 00:01:17.710
So‘ng adapterni GridView ga 
o‘rnatishimiz mumkin.

00:01:17.710 --> 00:01:21.098
Keling endi ilovani ishga tushirib, qanday ko‘rinishga kelishini kuzatamiz.

00:01:21.098 --> 00:01:23.270
Xo‘sh, endi Numbers activity ni bosgach,

00:01:23.270 --> 00:01:25.580
biz ikkita so‘zlardan iborat ustunlarni 
ko‘rishimiz mumkin. 

00:01:25.580 --> 00:01:28.730
Shunday qilib, har bir element
 avvalgidek bir xil layout ni ishlatyapti.

00:01:28.730 --> 00:01:32.360
Bizda vertikal linear layout bor, va 
 Miwok so‘zi tepada, 

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:33.900
Inglizcha so‘z esa pastda.

00:01:33.900 --> 00:01:37.150
Farqi faqat shundaki, butun ekran
 kengligini egallash o‘rniga,

00:01:37.150 --> 00:01:41.030
har bir element faqat ekranning yarmini oladi.

00:01:41.030 --> 00:01:44.260
chunki, aytganimizdek, biz ikkita 
ustunli grid xohlagan edik.

00:01:44.260 --> 00:01:47.500
Ko‘rishimiz mumkinki, ArrayAdapter ning
 mantiqi bir xil bo‘lib qolaveradi,

00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:50.540
u ListView yoki GridView ga
 biriktirilgan bo‘lsa ham.

00:01:50.540 --> 00:01:54.220
Adapter elementlar view larini so‘zlar ro‘yxatini 
to‘g‘ri tarkibi bilan yaratishi mumkin 

00:01:54.220 --> 00:01:59.365
va ListView yoki GridView ularni 
ekranga joylashtiradi.

00:01:59.365 --> 00:02:03.125
Umid qilamanki, mana shu mashqlar adapter ko‘rinishlarni 
yaxshiroq tushunishga yordam berdi.

00:02:03.125 --> 00:02:06.315
Endi men GridView da kiritgan o‘zgarishlarni
bekor qilib, listView ishlatishga qaytaman.

